<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Feedback Form Landing Page</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <style>
    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    body {
      font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
      background: #f7f7f7;
      color: #333;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    header {
      background: #fff;
      padding: 80px 20px 40px;
      text-align: center;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
    }

    header h1 {
      font-size: 3rem;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    header p {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      color: #666;
    }

    .cta-section {
      background: #ff385c;
      color: #fff;
      padding: 40px 20px;
      text-align: center;
      border-radius: 16px;
      margin: 40px auto;
      max-width: 900px;
    }

    .cta-section h2 {
      font-size: 1.8rem;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .btn {
      background: #fff;
      color: #ff385c;
      padding: 14px 32px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 1rem;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      border: 2px solid transparent;
    }

    .btn:hover {
      background: transparent;
      color: #fff;
      border: 2px solid #fff;
    }

    .features-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
      gap: 30px;
      padding: 40px 20px;
      max-width: 1000px;
      margin: auto;
    }

    .feature-card {
      background: #fff;
      padding: 30px 20px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
      text-align: center;
    }

    .feature-card h3 {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      color: #ff385c;
    }

    .feature-card p {
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      color: #555;
    }

    footer {
      background: #fff;
      color: #888;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 30px 20px;
      margin-top: 40px;
      box-shadow: 0 -2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
    }

    .social-links a {
      margin: 0 10px;
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      color: #ff385c;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .social-links a:hover {
      color: #333;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <h1>Welcome to Our Feedback Platform</h1>
    <p>Your voice matters! Help us create a better experience by sharing your valuable feedback.</p>
  </header>

  <section class="cta-section">
    <h2>Ready to Share Your Thoughts?</h2>
    <a href="/register" class="btn">Get Started</a>
  </section>

  <section class="features-grid">
    <div class="feature-card">
      <h3>Real Impact</h3>
      <p>Your feedback directly influences our improvements and helps us serve you better.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-card">
      <h3>Easy to Use</h3>
      <p>Simple and intuitive interface makes providing feedback quick and effortless.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-card">
      <h3>Secure & Private</h3>
      <p>Your responses are confidential and protected with industry-standard security.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <footer>
    <div class="social-links">
      <a href="#">Facebook</a>
      <a href="#">Twitter</a>
      <a href="#">LinkedIn</a>
      <a href="#">Instagram</a>
    </div>
    <p>&copy; 2024 Feedback Platform. All rights reserved.</p>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
